Package net.dean.jraw

Contains JRAW's major classes

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Endpoint
    This class represents a Reddit API endpoint such as "POST /api/login"
    JrawUtils
    A collection of utility methods
    OAuth2RedditClient
    This class provides a way to interact with the Reddit API using OAuth2.
    RedditClient
    This class provides a gateway to the services this library provides
    RedditClient.SubmissionRequest
    This class is used by RedditClient.getSubmission(net.dean.jraw.RedditClient.SubmissionRequest) to specify the parameters of the request.
    Version
    This class provides a standard way to version the library
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Endpoints
    This class is an automatically generated enumeration of Reddit's API endpoints
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ApiException
    This class provides a way to translate errors returned by the Reddit API into Java Exceptions
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    EndpointImplementation
    This annotation shows that this method is ultimately responsible for the implementation of a Reddit API endpoint (such as /api/login)
